B.QR=new A.hH("Craftechy App (Applicant App)","assets/images/Craftechy_website.png","Craftechy is a next-generation mobile platform built to simplify how users explore careers, connect with companies, and access professional services. Whether you're looking for a job, checking company projects, or submitting an application, Craftechy delivers a fast, user-friendly, and reliable experience.","System","Browse Jobs Easily Explore open positions with clear details, requirements, and benefits.\nApply in Seconds Submit applications directly inside the app with a smooth and intuitive workflow.\nTrack Company Projects Discover completed and ongoing projects to learn more about the company\u2019s work quality and capabilities.\nModern User Interface A clean, elegant UI optimized for speed, productivity, and user comfort.\nEducation & Services Section Access company services, training programs, and skill-enhancing opportunities.\nSmart Contact Options Contact the company through email, phone, or integrated forms with a single tap.\nSecure & Optimized Performance Built with high-quality code standards to ensure stability across all devices.","https://github.com/YoussefElqursh/Craftechy_app.git","https://drive.google.com/file/d/1mXOTeXgsCqX3kMqEVUjpLyJxFPfifyB0/view?usp=sharing",u.Z,B.oJ)
